videos.description: Northwestern center Dererk Pardon drives to the basket looking for a two-handed dunk, but Wisconsin guard Khalil Iverson rises up to blocked the shot, which gets the Badgers' bench on their feet.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wisconsin's Iverson emphatically stuffs dunk attempt in loss) 2017/02/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wisconsin's Iverson emphatically stuffs dunk attempt in loss

videos.description: After Northwestern forward Vic Law misses a layup, center Dererk Pardon quickly grabs the board and throws down a monster two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Northwestern's Pardon cleans up miss with dunk in win) 2017/02/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Northwestern's Pardon cleans up miss with dunk in win
